### Health check — debe mostrar db.status: "UP"
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Info de la aplicación
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Lista de métricas disponibles
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

###

### Memoria JVM usada
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used
Accept: application/json

###

### Conexiones activas de HikariCP
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.active
Accept: application/json

###

### Mappings (endpoints REST registrados)
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/mappings
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar todos los temas (datos de import.sql)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/temas-service/temas
Accept: application/json

###